# 1. Directory Structure

Your files are already in the correct place (user home). Hereâ€™s the structure for reference:

```
playbook.yml
inventory
vars/
  main.yml
group_vars/
  all.yml
roles/
  preflight_checks/
    tasks/main.yml
  primary_prep/
    tasks/main.yml
  file_transfer/
    tasks/main.yml
  standby_config/
    tasks/main.yml
  rman_duplicate/
    tasks/main.yml
  activation_validation/
    tasks/main.yml
  finalization/
    tasks/main.yml
  post_validation/
    tasks/main.yml
  error_handling/
    tasks/main.yml
templates/
  tnsnames.ora.j2
  listener.ora.j2
  rman_duplicate_script.j2
```

